And you can see, even in this wonderful,
large Steinway piano,

75
00:05:54.399 --> 00:05:58.832
you have a clarity of sound and
even more expansive range, and

76
00:05:58.832 --> 00:06:02.690
especially color because
of the cross-stringing.

